column18:
Thank you for participating in the first wave of the 2018-2019 CORE study! We truly appreciate your help, which is essential to the project’s success; and so is your feedback!

 

To receive your Amazon gift card, you will need to do the following.


	Complete and return the Gift Card form (see next item on survey). This only needs to be done ONE time.
	Complete the survey. There will be a new survey after each wave of testing, and each one will take you no more than 5 minutes to complete.


 

Please enter your district email address to get started.
column19:
You will need to complete and return the form below to receive your Amazon gift card.

Please click the link and complete and return the form.



Gift Card Form - CORE 2018-19
